thread.title: ‘Maze Runner’ Sequel Scorches Competition

author: Ben Fritz
title: ‘Maze Runner’ Sequel Scorches Competition
text:
Continuing a string of young-adult films that haven’t done quite as well as expected in the past year, Twentieth Century Fox’s second “Maze Runner” movie opened slightly lower than the original.
